165
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,870
Wasn't Dad's last lesson enough?

166
00:13:50,990 --> 00:13:52,200
I'll teach you a real lesson.

167
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:53,410
And

168
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:55,240
