248
00:21:10,990 --> 00:21:11,830
Because...

249
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:14,580
Chu is Lanshan.
[*Blue Mountain, or Lanshan in Chinese]

250
00:21:16,830 --> 00:21:18,120
